title: Chocolate Espresso Torte - The Blended Life | KitchenAid
description:
This Chocolate Espresso Torte is chocolate decadance created at the speed of blending. Watch how Tess Masters of The Blender Girl uses dairy-free ingredients and the Variable Speed Dial to achieve the silky, smooth torte texture.
